snippet.title: SWIV 3D gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for SWIV 3D (aka swiv 3d - temperate zone), Dos PC game produced by SCi Games in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/swiv-3d/1661/
In this video I am completing the first mission of the game and playing a little of the second one. A really fun to play game which I am recommending to all the lovers of this genre.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
